 Critical Rate, bisa ga fasaha. \n- {@green} Shamaki{@DEFAULT}: Yana ƙin lalacewa daidai da shingen HP. \n- {@green} Tunani{@DEFAULT}: Karɓi kashi 80% na lalacewa kawai daga abokan gaba, kuma a mayar da kashi 20% ga maharin. \n- {@green} Immune{@DEFAULT}: Yana da rigakafi ga duk illar cutarwa. Ba a cire illolin da ke faruwa a yanzu. \n- {@green} Absorption na HP{@DEFAULT}: Mai da kashi 10% na lalacewar da aka yiwa abokan gaba a matsayin HP.',
